nodes.text: Resik was a male Jillsarian bartender at the Broken Tusk circa 6 ABY. Having been harassed multiple times by the Galactic Empire, Resik was an occasional informant to the Rebel Alliance and later New Republic. He notified Eedund Cus about the cadaver clause in Lobar Aybock's shockboxing contract with Torel Vorne.
